# TreehouseCMS conventions

- Read `README.md` before making code changes in this repo.
- Keep business invariants in Strapi lifecycle hooks/services, not duplicated in clients.
- When review records change (create/update/delete/moderate), keep product review summary stats in sync.
- Prefer idempotent recompute logic for aggregate stats to avoid drift.
- Handle reassignment cases by updating aggregates for both previous and current product slugs.
- Keep admin moderation actions aligned with review visibility rules (`reviewStatus`, `isPublishedToSite`).
